## Quick Start

```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py shell < add_sample_data.py
python manage.py runserver
```

Then visit: http://127.0.0.1:8000/graphql/

